General Rules
Variables and functions: camelCase
Components and classes: PascalCase
Files and folders: kebab-case (except component files use PascalCase)
Constants: SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE
Hooks: camelCase starting with "use"
Examples for Copilot
javascript
// Variables - camelCase
const userName = "";
const isLoading = false;
const apiResponse = {};

// Functions - camelCase  
const handleClick = () => {};
const getUserData = () => {};
const validateForm = () => {};

// Components - PascalCase
const UserProfile = () => {};
const LoginForm = () => {};
const NavigationBar = () => {};

// Hooks - camelCase with "use" prefix
const useAuth = () => {};
const useLocalStorage = () => {};
const useFetch = () => {};

// Classes - PascalCase
class ApiService {}
class UserManager {}

// Constants - SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE
const API_BASE_URL = "";
const MAX_RETRY_ATTEMPTS = 3;
File Naming
Component files: UserProfile.tsx, LoginForm.tsx
Hook files: useAuth.tsx, useMobile.tsx
Utility files: api-service.ts, auth-utils.ts
Config files: constants.ts, api-config.ts
Folders: components/, user-profile/, auth-forms/
Quick Reference
React component? → PascalCase
Custom hook? → camelCase + "use" prefix
Regular variable/function? → camelCase
File contains component? → PascalCase.tsx
Utility/config file? → kebab-case.ts
Folder? → kebab-case


